            <p class="mb-0">This is a random message wich is visible only after a user (doesnt mather if its logged on or not) clicks the GET MESSAGE button</p>
            <footer class="blockquote-footer">
                Someone from <cite title="Source Title">name of country that the message originates from</cite>. <br />
